title: Guyver: Dark Hero (1994 Sci-Fi) The ultimate weapon.

sources.title: Guyver: Dark Hero (1994 Sci-Fi) The ultimate weapon.
sources.description:
Sean Barker's back in the alien armor! When a mysterious artifact lures him to an archaeological dig, he uncovers a conspiracy involving mutant Zoanoids and ancient alien tech. And must fight the Kronos Corporation.  Can the bio armour known as the Guyver stop a new breed of monsters before they unleash hell?  

Director: Steve Wang
Writers: Nathan Long, Steve Wang, Yoshiki Takaya
Creature Effects by Steve Wang & Matt Rose  
Genres: Action, Horror, Sci-Fi, Thriller

Main cast:
David Hayter as Sean Barker / Guyver  
Kathy Christopherson as Cori  
Bruno Patrick as Crane  
Christopher Michael as Atkins  
Stuart Weiss as Lisker  
Jimmie F. Skaggs as Colonel Castle  
Michael Berryman as Zimmerman  
Jim Lau as Dr. Tetsu Segawa
